  <h4>I forgot my password, what do I do? </h4>
  <h6>Yes, we are currently implementing a forgot password feature that should make it's debut in the upcoming few weeks. </h6>

  <h4>Can I change my workout profile preferences?</h4> 
  <h6>Yes, you can simply click on the row in the table of the workout you want to change and use the dialog box that's presented to change your preferences. Make sure you hit "Save Changes" though</h6>

